## CSS Organization

### Application Stylesheet

```css
/* app/assets/stylesheets/application.css */

/* Tailwind directives */
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

/* Custom component styles */
@layer components {
  .btn-primary {
    @apply bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg;
    @apply hover:bg-blue-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500;
    @apply transition-colors;
  }
}

/* Custom utilities */
@layer utilities {
  .text-shadow {
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
}
```

### Multiple Stylesheets

```css
/* app/assets/stylesheets/application.css - Main app styles */
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

/* app/assets/stylesheets/admin.css - Admin-specific styles */
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

@layer components {
  .admin-sidebar {
    @apply w-64 bg-gray-800 text-white;
  }
}
```

```erb
<!-- Load different stylesheets per layout -->
<!-- app/views/layouts/application.html.erb -->
<%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>

<!-- app/views/layouts/admin.html.erb -->
<%= stylesheet_link_tag "admin", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
```

